				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Barcus runs up to Wulbren in Haven after Wulbren is released from MOO. This is the culmination of everything he's been working for for the whole game and is so excited to see his friend - and find out what the deal wis with the runepowder plot. Barcus is swiftly rebuked by Wulbren and left disappointed but trying to save face."
